sources.title: Dead On Arrival | Full Crime Thriller Movie
sources.description:
Dead On Arrival - A pharmaceutical sales rep visits a small town in Louisiana on business. He finds himself in a dark world of corruption and murder with 24 hours to live, running from the police, the mob and a sheriff that wants him dead.
2017.  Stars: Christa B. Allen, Scottie Thompson, D.B. Sweeney
